have a role?

21:25.818 --> 21:27.953 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
ANGELA STENT, GEORGETOWN
UNIVERSITY: I think
we have to go back to 2011.

21:27.987 --> 21:33.692 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
