hoaxes that
were made up out of whole cloth.

38:07.352 --> 38:10.522 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SREENIVASAN: Now, people have
been trying
to fix the fake news problem.

38:10.555 --> 38:14.559 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
