false, even
though it looks just like an ABC
news site?

39:28.499 --> 39:31.502 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
OREMUS: Yes, I mean, that's a
good question,
and this is really the trickiest
question

39:31.536 --> 39:32.570 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
on this whole thing.

39:32.604 --> 39:34.505 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This is going to be an issue for
Facebook,
too.

39:34.539 --> 39:38.676 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
