check organizations
says this story has some parts
that are true,

39:38.710 --> 39:40.178 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
some parts that are false.

39:40.211 --> 39:42.013 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Is that a fake news story?

39:42.046 --> 39:45.183 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think what we've done and in
fact it seems
what Facebook has done as well
