counts as fake.

39:47.518 --> 39:48.987 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It's not just a story that might
be misleading.

39:49.020 --> 39:50.088 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
SREENIVASAN: Yes.

39:50.121 --> 39:51.990 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
OREMUS: Or has a couple of
factual errors
in it.

39:52.023 --> 39:57.061 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
