40:06.237 --> 40:09.374 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
third-party site that has used
evidence to
debunk that.

40:09.407 --> 40:12.110 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We're not going to be, you know,
doing the
debunking ourselves.

40:12.143 --> 40:15.713 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SREENIVASAN: Can technology
solve this problem?

40:15.747 --> 40:21.719 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
