fake.

40:23.688 --> 40:24.656 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
OREMUS: Yes.

40:24.689 --> 40:26.557 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
No, technology can't solve the
whole problem.

40:26.591 --> 40:29.560 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I think technology can be a part
of the solution.

40:29.594 --> 40:32.930 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
