a technological
problem or just a human problem.

40:32.964 --> 40:37.402 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And there are human issues at
work here in
why fake news is shared.

40:37.435 --> 40:38.603 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
