to be true.

40:40.905 --> 40:42.106 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I mean, you want something to be
true.

40:42.140 --> 40:43.241 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
SREENIVASAN: Yes.

40:43.274 --> 40:45.076 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
OREMUS: What's your incentive to
go and check
it out.

40:45.109 --> 40:48.446 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
