solution.

41:12.670 --> 41:14.372 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
But it has to be human, too.

41:14.405 --> 41:18.176 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
SREENIVASAN: That and a
